    {
      "id": "palm.three_talents.definition",
      "domain": "palm",
      "topic": "palm_lines",
      "originalText": "三才紋者，乃掌中三大紋也。",
      "normalizedClaim": "《神相全编》卷八把掌中三大纹称为三才纹。",
      "sourceRefIds": ["sxqb-shidian-v8-three-talents"],
      "interpretationStatus": "transcription_witness_scan_crosscheck_pending",
      "runtimePolicy": "cultural_learning_with_citation",
      "runtimeEligible": true
    },
    {
      "id": "palm.three_talents.names_and_associations",
      "domain": "palm",
      "topic": "palm_lines",
      "originalText": "第一紋居火，為天紋，主根基；第二紋居土，為地紋，主財祿；第三紋居明堂，為人紋，主福德。",
      "normalizedClaim": "该卷从上至下列天纹、地纹、人纹及其传统关联；此处没有建立与现代感情线、生命线、智慧线名称的一一对应。",
      "sourceRefIds": ["sxqb-shidian-v8-three-talents", "sxqb-shidian-v8-palm-three-lines"],
      "interpretationStatus": "transcription_witness_mapping_boundary",
      "runtimePolicy": "cultural_learning_with_citation",
      "runtimeEligible": true
    },
    {
      "id": "palm.fingers.generic_form_associations",
      "domain": "palm",
      "topic": "finger_form",
      "originalText": "指纖而長者，聰俊；指短而突者，愚賤。指柔而密者，蓄積；指硬而疏者，破敗。",
      "normalizedClaim": "《神相全编》卷八确有笼统的指形长短、柔硬与传统判断，但未把食指、无名指、小指分别映射到旧库的现代能力标签。",
      "sourceRefIds": ["sxqb-shidian-v8-finger-form"],
      "interpretationStatus": "transcription_witness_scan_crosscheck_pending",
      "runtimePolicy": "cultural_learning_with_citation",
      "runtimeEligible": true
